{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-gatsby-templates-wiki-tsx","path":"/wiki/vuejs/","result":{"data":{"file":{"fields":{"gitLogs":[{"hash":"ee34ec929ca5967011a21066c20f3f1b9f8c7fbe","date":"2023-07-22T21:53:32Z"},{"hash":"e8b5e5e97e4424ec69197ec702460b61e8880cef","date":"2023-01-01T15:11:35Z"},{"hash":"cb66b384193b180e61f0246295e6b58cb044cbce","date":"2023-01-01T13:30:51Z"}]},"childMarkdownRemark":{"headings":[{"value":"Vue JS"}],"fields":{"slug":"/vuejs/","relatedDocs":[]},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#vue-js\">Vue JS</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#transition\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;transition></code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<h1 id=\"vue-js\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vue-js\" aria-label=\"vue js permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vue JS</h1>\n<h2 id=\"transition\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#transition\" aria-label=\"transition permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;transition></code></h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;transition></code>을 이용한 모달 컴포넌트:<br>\n<a href=\"https://kr.vuejs.org/v2/examples/modal.html\">https://kr.vuejs.org/v2/examples/modal.html</a></p>\n<p>transition 컴포넌트 설명:<br>\n<a href=\"https://kr.vuejs.org/v2/guide/transitions.html\">https://kr.vuejs.org/v2/guide/transitions.html</a></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;transition></code> 안에 엘리먼트를 작성하면\n<code class=\"language-text\">transition</code> 컴포넌트로 출력/감춤에 대한 다양한 상태를 관리할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;transition name=\"FOO\">\n  &lt;div>Hello&lt;/div>\n&lt;/transition></code></pre></div>\n<p>단순히 컨텐츠를 wrapping만 하고, CSS로 여러가지 일을 할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.FOO-enter</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.FOO-leave-active</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.FOO-enter .FOO-container,\n.FOO-leave-active .FOO-container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 CSS를 설정하고 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;transition></code> 태그를\n<code class=\"language-text\">v-if</code> 등으로 감추고 출력해보면 CSS에 명세한 애니메이션이 적용된다.</p>"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"gitHubRepositoryUrl":"https://github.com/edunga1/cat-logic"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4e3d9aa2-5c9c-54bc-9319-dc0ee8ca64f4"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}